Get it:
 * wget http://github.com/onjin/django-buildout-template/tarball/v1.0.2
 * unpack && cd in

Use virtualenv for better isolation:
 * virtualenv --no-site-packages ./env
 * source ./env/bin/activate
 * easy_install -U setuptools

if not exists boostrap.py:
 * "wget http://svn.zope.org/*checkout*/zc.buildout/trunk/bootstrap/bootstrap.py
then:
 * python bootstrap.py

build it:
 * ./bin/buildout
 * or simple use 'make'

install:
 * ./bin/django-prod syncdb

run:
 * ./bin/django-(prod/dev) runserver

Let's rule:
 * git init
 * git add .gitignore bootstrap.py buildout.cfg 
 * git commit -m '@init'

test
